&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;I think this is entirely possible since TSS will be the new expansion with all new content for levels 1-75, and all the older players will be flooding into the expansion to check it out.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
